##Bitcoin sub-units



|1.00 |One bitcoin (abbreviation BTC)
|0.01 |One bitcent
|0.001 |One millibitcoin (nickname "Millie")
|0.000001 |One microbitcoin (nickname "Mike")
|0.00000001 |One satoshi (the minimum Bitcoin base unit)


This terminology is unofficial, but the terms "bitcent" and "satoshi" seem to have been accepted into common usage.

